Titolo: BloodRayne 2

Anno: 2004

Descrizione: BloodRayne 2 is an action hack and slash video game developed by Terminal Reality for PlayStation 2, Xbox and Microsoft Windows. It does not follow on directly from where BloodRayne finished; instead, it takes place 60 and 70 years later in a contemporary 2000s setting.
This game was re-released as BloodRayne 2: Terminal Cut on November 20, 2020. BloodRayne 2 will also be released on PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox One and Nintendo Switch as BloodRayne 2: ReVamped on November 18, 2021.